{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then later on the German radio-- of course, the Nazi radio distorted everything and said, you know, some traitors, a group of traitors has tried to assassinate the Fuhrer, but God has protected him.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He didn't believe in God, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So but the superior powers have protected the Fuhrer, and all those--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, traitors will all be severely punished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will all be executed, every one of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were hung up on meat hooks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- and Hitler had taken a film of them, and he wanted to see that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had it shown to him later so he could have the satisfaction to see that they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that's pretty, pretty awful to people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, they could have shot them or could have hanged them, but they actually hung them up on meat hooks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were people on the-- so that's, that ended that period.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now I'm waiting for an assignment from the employment department because I can't think-- everybody-- I was in forced labor in the factory in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did they miss me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they didn't miss me because in October, I get another summons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This time it says, you are to report for embarkation at the Grunewald station, railroad station, for shipment to the-- to a-- I don't think they said forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, to a camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think they said anything about the camp, about the nature of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to report there at 7 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that's what I-- you know, that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I, I had no idea what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
